Name: ASU Global
About the game: The beginning of an exciting MMORPG. Start a new adventure in the world of A.S.U. ▶ Game Introduction Here is a world that needs your help. The dark god Exilis is about to destroy the world with a powerful force. Anitas, the god of light, fights against Exilis, but lacks strength. We need your help to save the world from destruction. Your help goes a long way in saving the world. Join now. ▶ Characteristic - Stylish MMORPG - Party play with a combination of 5 unique classes. - Battle with huge and powerful field boss monsters. - Guardian system that gets stronger the more you combine it. - Guild system that gets stronger as you grow.
